      --report Output/candidate_validation/stage7_merge_report.json

  What it does:
  1. Loads v2_preview.json and stage4_findings.json
  2. Excludes blocking findings (Sprint planning) and LOW confidence entries
  3. Shows overlap analysis — entries already in canonical_data.json
  4. For overlaps: merges new aliases into existing entries
  5. For new entries: adds under their tag/group
  6. Writes sorted merged output and a detailed merge report